     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>¶ The authour to the Christian readers.</head>
   <l>¶ Because I was in Fraunce, which is so wyde,</l>
   <l>Borne &amp; brought vp, &amp; not in y<seg rend="sup">t</seg> English</l>
   <l>Sins my birthes dai, as other writers be</l>
   <l>Learned and taught: do I earnestlye,</l>
   <l>Now you al that in England do dwell,</l>
   <l>And professe Christ, y<seg rend="sup">t</seg> euer springing wel</l>
   <l>Desyre and pray, to take in good worth,</l>
   <l>That I haue here wrought &amp; set furthe.</l>
</div>
